# --- Vercel: set these in Project → Settings → Environment Variables (Production) ---
#
# Production canonical URL — primary host is WWW (https, no trailing slash).
# Must match your Google Search Console URL-prefix property and the Vercel production domain.
# Used for metadataBase, sitemap.xml, robots.txt, and apex → www redirect.
# Production (this site): https://www.palmsplacecondos.com — no trailing slash; must match Vercel production domain + GSC URL-prefix property.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=https://www.palmsplacecondos.com

# Google Search Console — HTML tag verification (paste the content value only, not the full meta tag).
# GOOGLE_SITE_VERIFICATION=...
# Or: NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_SITE_VERIFICATION=...

# Palms Place Facebook page (footer “Facebook” link; optional override of site-contact default)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FACEBOOK_URL=https://www.facebook.com/palmsplace

# YouTube channel or handle URL (footer “YouTube” link)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_YOUTUBE_URL=https://www.youtube.com/@YourChannel

# RealScout office listings widget (optional; default agent id is in code)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_REALSCOUT_AGENT_ENCODED_ID=QWdlbnQtMjI1MDUw

# Dr. Jan Duffy — curated RealScout home search (shared search link sitewide)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_REALSCOUT_SHARED_SEARCH_URL=https://drjanduffy.realscout.com/homesearch/shared-searches/...

# Homepage “Just listed” banner — optional override for the featured listing detail URL (RealScout).
# NEXT_PUBLIC_FEATURED_LISTING_URL=https://drjanduffy.realscout.com/homesearch/listings/p-4381-w-flamingo-road-822-las-vegas-89103-glvartrestle-932

# JSON-LD sameAs — comma-separated profile URLs (optional extras).
# Facebook, YouTube, and Google Business Profile from site-contact.ts are merged automatically.
# Must match real outbound links on the site; omit if not yet published.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SAME_AS_URLS=https://www.youtube.com/@YourChannel,https://share.google/...

# JSON-LD — absolute URL for agent/team photo (RealEstateAgent / LocalBusiness image). Omit until asset is live.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_AGENT_IMAGE_URL=https://www.yourdomain.com/images/your-photo.jpg

# Open Graph / Twitter link preview (1200×630 JPG or PNG). Omit to use auto-generated /opengraph-image.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_OG_IMAGE_URL=https://www.palmsplacecondos.com/images/og-palms-place.jpg

# JSON-LD — optional office geocoordinates (must match Google Business Profile map pin for office address).
# NEXT_PUBLIC_OFFICE_LAT=36.1147
# NEXT_PUBLIC_OFFICE_LNG=-115.1728

# Contact page — optional iframe embed URL override. Do NOT use Google My Maps
# (`https://www.google.com/maps/d/embed?mid=...`) — unpublished mids 404 with
# “404. That’s an error” inside the iframe. Prefer Maps Embed API (below) or omit
# so the app uses the stable Google place embed from src/lib/maps-embed.ts.
# NEXT_PUBLIC_CONTACT_MAP_EMBED_URL=https://www.google.com/maps/embed?origin=mfe&pb=!1m2!2m1!1s3651+Lindell+Rd+Suite+D,+Las+Vegas,+NV+89103

# Google Maps Embed API key (place-mode iframe; free unlimited usage per Google).
# Recommended. Restrict the key to this domain (HTTP referrers) in Google Cloud Console.
# https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/embed/get-started
# NEXT_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_EMBED_API_KEY=...

# NAP (name, address, phone): add optional fields in src/lib/site-contact.ts when they match
# visible footer/contact copy and your Google Business Profile. JSON-LD telephone/address only
# emit when those fields are set (see src/lib/schema.ts).
